  "title": "Sports Journalist, Lianhe Zaobao",
  "description": "<p>As a Sports Journalist at Lianhe Zaobao, you will be the pulse of our sports coverage. We are looking for a candidate who is deeply knowledgeable about the sports landscape. This role requires individuals with a sharp nose for news who can produce rigorous, fact-based reporting for both print and digital platforms. You will ensure that all breaking news and commentaries are clear, concise and engaging for Lianhe Zaobao’s audiences across every channel.<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Degree in Journalism, Media, Chinese Studies or related discipline. Prior experience in news reporting is preferred but strong portfolio will be considered;</p></li><li><p>Effectively bilingual (English/Chinese), with excellent writing and conversational skills. You must demonstrate the ability to translate complex sports nuances into accurate, engaging Chinese content;</p></li><li><p>Strong interest in and passion for sports news (local and international) and current affairs;</p></li><li><p>Familiar with Social Media platforms. You must be able to adapt news content into social formats to drive engagement;</p></li><li><p>Competency in photography, video filming and editing is a distinct advantage;</p></li><li><p>A self-motivated and driven individual who possesses an inquisitive mind with a nose for news;</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently under pressure as well as collaborate effectively across teams;</p></li><li><p>Ability to multitask,  adapt to changes and willingness to work irregular hours to cover sporting events</p></li></ul>",
